      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:58:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过允许银行保留较小的准备金来刺激经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/pboc-will-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示将在两周内降低银行存款准备金率，并暗示将采取更多支持措施，这一异常提前的披露表明习近平主席政府提振经济和阻止 6 万亿美元股市暴跌的紧迫性越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/pboc-will-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:43:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
